  "decision_conditions": [
    "Reason: The proposed extensions by reason of their  inappropriate design, scale, massing, and bulk would form an overdominant and visually harmful feature when viewed from the surrounding streetscene. The development would harm the existing symmetry of the host pair at 52 & 54 Hillmarton Road and would fail to preserve or enhance the character and appearance of the host building or its setting within the wider Hillmarton Conservation Area. The development is therefore considered to be contrary to policy 9 of Islington’s Core Strategy 2011, policies D4 (Designing in context), D11 (Alterations and extensions), D26 & D27 (Side extensions), Islington’s Urban Design Guidance 2006, Hillmarton conservation guidance note and PPS 5."
